            "detailed_description": "Nancy Drew®: Danger by Design is a first-person perspective, point-and-click adventure game.  The player is Nancy Drew and has to solve a mystery. Explore rich environments for clues, interrogate suspects, and solve puzzles and mini-games.<br>\t\t\t\t\tFashion designer Minette might be at the height of her career, but rumors have been flying about her bizarre behavior.  Is this designer diva coming apart at the seams, or is someone keeping her spring collection unfashionably behind schedule?  It’s up to you, as Nancy Drew, to travel to Paris for an internship and sew up this case in style!<br>\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover the inner workings of the fashion industry.<br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Experience Parisian life—dining at a café, translating French, and riding the Metro.<br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Skin dive and snoop around the creepy catacombs.<br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Haggle with merchants for souvenirs.<br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Solve puzzles based on concocting parfaits, developing photos, and completing circuit boards.<br>\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Erase mistakes by using the ‘Second Chance’ feature.<br>\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul> <br>\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About The Nancy Drew Adventure Series</h2>\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/31930/extras/ND_logo.jpg\" ><br>The original #1 selling PC adventure series. <br>See a <a href=\"http://storefront.steampowered.com/v/gfx/apps_extras/NancyDrewCompare/english.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >comparison</a> of the Dossier and Adventure Series",
